text: Jessica Jones Wins a Bar Fight in This Kickass New Teaser Pour one out for the victims of Krysten Ritter's bar fight!In the newly released trailer for ... Comment   8:10 PM Updated at 11:01 PM   8:10 PM Updated at 11:01 PM Â» Social News Pour one out for the victims of Krysten Ritter 's bar fight! In the newly released trailer for Marvel's Jessica Jones , we see her doing a victory shot after taking down a full bar of bad guys. Sadly, we don't see her showing off her super powers -- which include super strength and the ability to fly -- but clearly she knows how to handle herself against goons! The Netflix exclusive is part of their ongoing deal with Marvel. They just released some promo shots a couple of weeks ago, and it looks amazing . All 13 episodes of Jessica Jones will be released on Friday, Nov. 20 on Netflix. By TV Guide
